.TP
.B \-\-wait\-interval\-seconds [integer]
.UNINDENT
.sp
Check every \fB\-\-wait\-interval\-seconds\fP to see whether the resource to see if it has reached the lifecycle state defined by \fB\-\-wait\-for\-state\fP\&. Defaults to 30 seconds.
